metrics_conclusion: In terms of chords and melody, Hello is more complex than the typical song, having above average scores in Melodic Complexity, Chord-Melody Tension, Chord Progression Novelty and Chord-Bass Melody.
key_conclusion: Hello has sections analyzed in the following keys: A Major,  and A Mixolydian.  Click on the linked cheat sheets for popular chords, chord progressions, downloadable midi files and more!

metadata.editComments: Despite the C# and D notes in the background melody throughout, I think these chords would be best expressed as simply A and Dm.
